<p><b>Queen Elizabeth</b> or <b>Queen Elisabeth</b> may refer to:</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Queens_regnant">Queens regnant</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Queen_Elizabeth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Queens regnant">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_I_of_England" title="Elizabeth I of England">Elizabeth I of England</a> (1533每1603), last Tudor monarch over England, reigned 1558每1603</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_II" title="Elizabeth II">Elizabeth II</a> (born 1926) of the United Kingdom and the other Commonwealth Realms, reigning since 1952</li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Queens_consort.2C_dowager_and_mother">Queens consort, dowager and mother</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Queen_Elizabeth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Queens consort, dowager and mother">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Queen_Elizabeth_The_Queen_Mother" title="Queen Elizabeth The Queen Mother">Elizabeth Bowes-Lyon</a> (1900每2002), queen consort, queen dowager and queen mother of the United Kingdom (known from 1952 until her death as <i>Queen Elizabeth The Queen Mother</i>)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_Woodville" title="Elizabeth Woodville">Elizabeth Woodville</a> (1437每1492), queen consort, queen dowager and queen mother of England</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_of_Aragon" title="Elizabeth of Aragon">Elizabeth of Aragon</a> (1271每1336), queen consort, queen dowager and queen mother of Portugal</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_of_Austria_(1436%E2%80%931505)" title="Elisabeth of Austria (1436每1505)" class="mw-redirect">Elisabeth of Austria (1436每1505)</a>, queen consort, queen dowager and queen mother of Poland</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_of_Bavaria" title="Elisabeth of Bavaria" class="mw-redirect">Elisabeth of Bavaria</a> (1837每1898), queen consort of Hungary, Croatia, and Bohemia</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_of_Bavaria_(1876%E2%80%931965)" title="Elisabeth of Bavaria (1876每1965)" class="mw-redirect">Elisabeth of Bavaria (1876每1965)</a>, queen consort, queen dowager and queen mother of the Belgians</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_of_Bohemia_(1292%E2%80%931330)" title="Elisabeth of Bohemia (1292每1330)" class="mw-redirect">Elisabeth of Bohemia (1292每1330)</a>, queen consort of Bohemia</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_of_Bohemia_(1358%E2%80%931373)" title="Elisabeth of Bohemia (1358每1373)">Elisabeth of Bohemia (1358每1373)</a>, queen consort of the Romans, Hungary, and Bohemia</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_of_Bohemia" title="Elizabeth of Bohemia" class="mw-redirect">Elizabeth of Bohemia</a> (1596每1662), the "Winter Queen", briefly queen consort of Bohemia, wife of Frederick V, Elector Palatine</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_of_Bosnia" title="Elizabeth of Bosnia">Elizabeth of Bosnia</a> (1340每1387), queen consort and queen dowager of Hungary and Poland, queen mother of Hungary</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_de_Burgh" title="Elizabeth de Burgh">Elizabeth de Burgh</a> (1289每1327), queen consort of Scotland</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_Richeza_of_Poland" title="Elisabeth Richeza of Poland" class="mw-redirect">Elisabeth Richeza of Poland</a> (1286每1335), queen consort of Bohemia and Poland</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_of_Romania" title="Elisabeth of Romania">Elisabeth of Romania</a> (1894每1956), queen consort of the Hellenes</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elisabeth_of_Wied" title="Elisabeth of Wied">Elisabeth of Wied</a> (1843每1916), queen consort and queen dowager of Romania</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Elizabeth_of_York" title="Elizabeth of York">Elizabeth of York</a> (1466每1503), queen consort of England</li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Queens_in_fiction">Queens in fiction</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Queen_Elizabeth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Queens in fiction">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Elizabeth III of the House of Winton, monarch of the Star Kingdom of Manticore, in David Weber's <a href="/wiki/Honorverse" title="Honorverse">Honorverse</a> books</li>
<li>Elizabeth X, aka "Liz Ten", fictional queen of <i>Starship UK</i> in the <i>Doctor Who</i> episode "<a href="/wiki/The_Beast_Below" title="The Beast Below">The Beast Below</a>"</li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Ships">Ships</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Queen_Elizabeth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Ships">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/HMS_Queen_Elizabeth" title="HMS Queen Elizabeth">HMS <i>Queen Elizabeth</i></a>, several ships of the Royal Navy</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/MS_Queen_Elizabeth" title="MS Queen Elizabeth">MS <i>Queen Elizabeth</i></a>, Cunard cruise ship launched in 2010</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/RMS_Queen_Elizabeth" title="RMS Queen Elizabeth">RMS <i>Queen Elizabeth</i></a>, Cunard ocean liner launched 1938, retired 1968</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/RMS_Queen_Elizabeth_2" title="RMS Queen Elizabeth 2" class="mw-redirect">RMS <i>Queen Elizabeth 2</i></a>, Cunard ocean liner launched in 1969, retired 2008</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Queen_Elizabeth_class" title="Queen Elizabeth class"><i>Queen Elizabeth</i> class</a>, several classes of ships</li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Other">Other</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Queen_Elizabeth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Other">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>"Queen Elizabeth" a nickname of one of two US <a href="/wiki/Presidential_State_Car_(United_States)" title="Presidential State Car (United States)" class="mw-redirect">Presidential limousines</a> of 1938</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Queen_Elizabeth_(band)" title="Queen Elizabeth (band)">Queen Elizabeth (band)</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Queen_Elizabeth,_Saskatoon" title="Queen Elizabeth, Saskatoon">Queen Elizabeth, Saskatoon</a>, a suburban neighborhood in the city of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, Canada</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Les_Amours_de_la_reine_%C3%89lisabeth" title="Les Amours de la reine 谷lisabeth">Les Amours de la reine 谷lisabeth</a></i> (<i>Queen Elizabeth</i>), 1912 film starring Sarah Bernhardt</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Queen_Elisabeth_Music_Competition" title="Queen Elisabeth Music Competition">Queen Elisabeth Music Competition</a></li>
</ul>
